會番番黎讀"},{"pid":"c54223ebe4e184e2eef02cc86af87e353a993244","tid":1079242,"uid":242554,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"275e441651fef86b1050f90b5387fd524635aa0e","tid":1079242,"uid":236242,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9b63df57db69d5fd43074d14f24585ef69331ee7","tid":1079242,"uid":242554,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"03b23d626020985d590202ad34bcce88e15a7f7e","tid":1079242,"uid":236242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T22:16:47.000Z","msg":"依加英國？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T22:21:35.000Z","msg":"努力地year2中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T22:23:58.000Z","msg":"唉 讀到好頹 又識唔到朋友 又掛住香港 想走人。<br />\n點解你又會番番黎讀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T22:41:21.000Z","msg":"識唔到朋友真係唔需要勉強，一來我唔飲酒，二來英國人對朋友嘅定義同我地真係唔同，無必要格硬融入。就算比你識到華人，其實黎外國係無用，加上好多（中國人）真係層次好低（sorry以偏概全但真係好大部分）。<br />\ndse一完就去英國，對英國呢個國家無乜了解就一枝公去咗，自然好多唔適應。<br />\nquit咗之後我返左香港做咗兩年嘢（sales），就會發現有必要堅持落去。<br />\n唔係話sales一定係低學歷低等，但當你自己知道自己有能力（至少language）嘅時候，仲同其他17/18歲小妹妹一樣人工、可能會係一樣未來嘅時候，就覺得至少要完成個degree。"},{"pid":"aa9c126e2c231b53cf7f6c392fc13581cdd8656c","tid":1079242,"uid":154557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"275e441651fef86b1050f90b5387fd524635aa0e","tid":1079242,"uid":236242,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9b63df57db69d5fd43074d14f24585ef69331ee7","tid":1079242,"uid":242554,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"03b23d626020985d590202ad34bcce88e15a7f7e","tid":1079242,"uid":236242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T22:16:47.000Z","msg":"依加英國？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T22:21:35.000Z","msg":"努力地year2中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T22:23:58.000Z","msg":"唉 讀到好頹 又識唔到朋友 又掛住香港 想走人。<br />\n點解你又會番番黎讀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T22:41:57.000Z","msg":"主動啲撩人吹水嘅話應該都識到朋友㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我year 1嗰陣又係成個毒摺咁唔敢同啲鬼講嘢，搞到讀得好頹。今年主動啲撩人吹水就識咗唔少人，有幾個仲幾fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1106df1ca6275e5e09e7df1ee78de2c78457f6c","tid":1079242,"uid":202198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"275e441651fef86b1050f90b5387fd524635aa0e","tid":1079242,"uid":236242,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9b63df57db69d5fd43074d14f24585ef69331ee7","tid":1079242,"uid":242554,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"03b23d626020985d590202ad34bcce88e15a7f7e","tid":1079242,"uid":236242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T22:16:47.000Z","msg":"依加英國？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T22:21:35.000Z","msg":"努力地year2中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T22:23:58.000Z","msg":"唉 讀到好頹 又識唔到朋友 又掛住香港 想走人。<br />\n點解你又會番番黎讀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T22:43:21.000Z","msg":"可以考慮去大學/學生會(Student Union)嘅輔導中心/Advice Centre問下，睇下佢哋有咩建議<br />\n<br />\n讀到好頹係咩方面？太忙太難？定太得閒無嘢做？<br />\n識朋友嘅話可以考慮join下club/society<br />\n<br />\nAnyway，就咁係連登討論傾下係無辦法完全解決問題，去返相關嘅大學/學生會Advice Centre親身同職員傾下先係最好辦法。有部分大學學生會係請返學生係呢啲centre做嘢，佢哋應該可以幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再唔係去同tutor/advisor討論下都係一個好方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：UG Year2，係某大學學生會嘅Advice Centre兼職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f507d63f2b21da9f748b1d777877de1a4c7b1c5","tid":1079242,"uid":180463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T22:47:08.000Z","msg":"識朋友真係好重要, 搵d興趣打發時間囉<br />\n自己係咁諗野只會愈來愈頹"},{"pid":"aa6f0697b490a319a81c8671b551052e75b93efd","tid":1079242,"uid":106992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f45ee150f78ef6983306ccb0176403b6c6f7748","tid":1079242,"uid":236242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T21:46:37.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇巴打試過係英國讀書頂唔順，讀左一年year1，番番香港讀U？"},"citedBy":0,